<br>
So I was stuck on the 4th isle for a while. Eventually I got bored and decided to call it a night since it was late and I had no way of going back up with a unrezzable corpse on 5th. I wanted to have some fun so I bust out the horse and try to jump off of the island with a horse. Well instead of falling, you float while on a horse. The thing about this float is that you don't float up or down. Basically the only way to float up is that you have to climb up on a hill or something like that and to float down, you have to click off the horse and free fall. <br>
<br>
Here is a picture of me floating in front of the 5th isle:<br>
<br>
<img src="http://members.aol.com/sugoishiro83/bug1"><br>
<br>
There was some island I didn't know what it was. It looked like there were some mobs on it but they were too far to target. Kind of looks like the 8th isle but smaller. It has a teleport pad on it too.<br>
<br>
<img src="http://members.aol.com/sugoishiro83/bug2"><br>
<br>
Fooling around enough times, I thought I could somehow float up to 5th isle to join the rest of my guildies. So after exploring the area a bit I tried for it. I failed a few times but eventually made it. I started off by climbing up the chain between the 5th and 7th isle.<br>
<br>
<img src="http://members.aol.com/sugoishiro83/bug3"><br>
<br>
I couldn't scale some of the chain links and I was still too low to float up to 5th isle so I floated all the way to the unknown island and climbed to the tip of the windmill. From there, I floated all the way back to the 4th isle and went to the windmill on that island. I was too low to get to the tip of it so I waited a bit and used the blades of the windmill to lift me to the tip. From there I went back to the same chain between 5th and 7th isle, climbed up a couple more links and was finally high enough to float to the 5th isle.<br>
<br>
<img src="http://members.aol.com/sugoishiro83/bug4"><br>
<br>
So with all that time I was able to get to the 5th isle to the 4th isle without a key and without getting rezzed to that island. I'm pretty sure that you can use a horse to float to other islands, just have to find the right path. This could save a ton of coffins and purchased keys while in air.<br>
<br>
I'm pretty sure someone else has figured this out. I don't read other sites too much so I don't know hehe. There are a few things about this though. I don't think the gms at all would like this if they found out about it. Another thing that is bad is that while exploring the space of poa, my horse disappeared all of a sudden and I fell on a chain for some fat falling damage. I know I didn't click it off, it just poofed for some reason. That is of course dangerous. And I cant stress this enough, you cant float down or up. So you cant take a horse from another island to the 1st island or anything like that. Once you are at a certain height, you are stuck on that vertical plane. Actually, that isn't entirely true, there are some places where I floated down a bit.<br>
<br>
Kind of fun to do this if you have a horse. Puts your money to use!<br>
